Radiant Health


























































Radiant Health


























About Us





Why Radiant Health
                   A healthcare company, that achieves superior business and brand performance by:
                  Enabling our people to enjoy realising their full potential
                  Employing a consumer centric approach to health and wellbeing
                  Helping our partners to deliver better health outcomes           
              
              


Business Model
                   Our business model is straightforward, whether we work as an agency, a distributor or combination thereof we work on a percentage of sales.
                    This very simply aligns the driver for us to maximise our performance, as we grow our partnerâs sales our income grows.
                    We agree with our partners what level of support their brands will enjoy and we report monthly on performance in market. 
                



Consumer-centric
                  Radiant Health is a healthcare company with a proven ability to drive superior sales and market share performance from mature Rx and consumer brands in the New Zealand market.
                    We employ a consumer/customer centric approach to health and wellbeing and we take the time to enjoy keeping it simple.
                



Strategies that deliver
                  Drawing on the enormous experience of our team we remain open minded to what our partners, customers and competitors are telling us.
                    We take the time and care to clearly identify the key issues and the strategies that will deliver superior performance. 
                    We formulate plans within an ROI framework and execute fast, always looking for the feedback that will enable us to refine and improve the execution.
                



Challenging the status quo
                  We challenge current thinking to deliver step changes in the way we deliver greater value to our customers and our partners. 
                    Please see our Enablers Section for three innovations that have delivered superior performance from a step change.
                



Keeping it simple
                  We manage all facets of our partners business within New Zealand and are seen very much as an extension of our partners in New Zealand.
                    Our primary objective is to make it as simple as possible for our partners while at the same time delivering superior results 
                    within a small but relatively complex market.        
                


















